<body>
    <h1>API Documentation</h1>
    <h2>User Routes</h2>
    <h3>GET /api/user</h3>
    <p>Returns a message indicating the User Route.</p>

    <h3>POST /api/user/register</h3>
    <p>Registers a new user. Requires the following fields:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>name: string (required)</li>
        <li>email: string (required)</li>
        <li>confirmEmail: string (required)</li>
        <li>password: string (required)</li>
        <li>confirmPassword: string (required)</li>
        <li>avatar: file (required)</li>
        <li>address: string (required)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>POST /api/user/verify-email</h3>
    <p>Verifies the user's email using an OTP. Requires the following field:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>otp: string (required)</li>
    </ul>
</body>
